headline: Why I Just Bought These 3 Ultra-High-Yield Dividend Stocks
summary: Dividend yields can be like ladders: The higher you go, the scarier it gets.  Many investors are more leery of ultra-high dividend yields because they're afraid the dividends could be in jeopardy.  Here are three ultra-high-yield dividend stocks I recently bought and why I like them.
